title: The Hanger Store 10 Childrens White Wooden Coat Hangers, For Baby & Toddler Clothes - Choose Colour
features: CHILDREN’S HANGER – Specialist 30cm wooden hanger designed for kids clothing, from newborn babies to toddlers, boys and girls. Perfect for shirts, jumpers, coats, jackets, baby grows and dresses.
MULTI-PURPOSE – Notches on arms allow for hanging items with loops, such as dresses and skirts, whilst integrated bar is perfect for storing child’s trousers.
SPACE SAVING – Flat design allows for maximum wardrobe storage, allowing more hangers on one rail. An essential item for a tidy and organised bedroom or nursery room.
QUALITY & DESIGN – Made using high quality strong wood for a long and useful lifespan. Classic design, available in natural or white, looks stylish and smart in all settings.
SWIVEL HOOK – 360-degree rotatable metal hook with anti-rust chrome plating.
description: 30 x 1.0cm Flat Wooden Childrens Suit Hanger with notches and bar. This children’s hanger is the cheapest wooden suit hanger in our wood range. It is ideal for both retailers and domestic customers who want children’s and adult hangers to match. But it also adds a touch of class for shops specialising in children’s clothes and to the nursery or child’s bedroom at home. A perfect gift for a new grandchild - it will long outlive the original garment! The notches and bar mean that this hanger can be used for hanging all types of garment – tops, shirts, skirts, trousers and suits.
